literals:
Math {

    Expression (an expression)
        = Expression "+" Term
        | Expression "-" Term
        | Term

    Term (a term)
        = Term "*" Factor
        | Term "/" Factor
        | Factor
    
    Factor
        = "(" Expression ")"
        | "+" Factor
        | "-" Factor
        | number
 
    number (an integer or floating point number)
        = digit* "." digit+     -- fract
        | digit+                -- whole
        }
